body:
Have you ever wondered where the ingredients are inserted into the brewing stand to create potions, this pack aims to answer that by altering the block's model by adding a "cup" on the top section of the stand, representing the input slot featured in its UI. The pack also changes the block's icon to reflect this altered design.

**Extra details**

- the current version of the pack is compatible with 1.21.9 to 26.1;
- the zip file can just be dragged and dropped in your "resourcepacks" folder, unzipping isn't required;
